  "description": "../description.md",
  "install_text": "The Cat-1 Asset Management Tracker unites multi-GNSS, BLE 5.0 and LTE Cat-1 for always-connected indoor & outdoor asset intelligence. Its twin 4 000 mAh Li-SOCl2 cells (8 000 mAh total) power up to 3+ years of adaptive reporting inside an IP68, palm-sized enclosure. Motion sensors, tamper switch and door-open detection transform raw position pings into actionable utilisation data—ideal for containers, transit cases and unattended machinery.",
